{"tid":1020852,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 情人節送咩禮物好","createTime":"2019-02-14T01:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T01:51:41.000Z","uid":207166,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dabf961d150942a1f8021cdfb7dcc414f380afc4","tid":1020852,"uid":207166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:03:22.000Z","msg":"雖然情人節應該係女仔送禮物比男仔<br />\n但因為小弟之前有幾次紀念日咩都冇準備<br />\n以致今次情人節佢要我補返數<br />\n佢講到明要收一張500字嘅卡<br />\n同一份好有心思嘅禮物<br />\n但小弟係一個完全冇創意嘅人<br />\n次次其他frd 生日我都係請佢食餐飯就算嗰啲<br />\n所以我今次真係拗爆頭<br />\n佢係嗰種唔鍾意物質 (錶/手袋/鞋 etc)<br />\n唔鍾意花 (嫌浪費)<br />\n鍾意啲可以keep 到好耐嘅嘢嘅人 <br />\n所以求各位巴打絲打俾啲意見小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65159d849d62147bb21cf931e589dad08324bf9e","tid":1020852,"uid":207166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:03:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e729a6f25ef1bf4abba1e1e940eeece3d6388270","tid":1020852,"uid":207166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:04:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32406d11cda41ca19b98ba24e4136def767eec9d","tid":1020852,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:04:55.000Z","msg":"講到明要咩禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4dfcceb0254553ebe20f5db7164d7e0433f1d9","tid":1020852,"uid":176169,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:07:01.000Z","msg":"男朋友成日要做運動 打下波果啲<br />\n見佢成日拎住個厚銀包好辛苦 <br />\n買咗個皮既卡套比佢<br />\n如果你女朋友又係鍾意做運動<br />\n又或者拎細袋多<br />\n可以考慮買個卡套比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f45dd5cddd1ae80f5c1c6376f64a30b6cc006e6c","tid":1020852,"uid":211060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:09:01.000Z","msg":"香水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29d1f7251480f780014e29bbb894e7119becc46","tid":1020852,"uid":207166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32406d11cda41ca19b98ba24e4136def767eec9d","tid":1020852,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:04:55.000Z","msg":"講到明要咩禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:10:51.000Z","msg":"之前聖誕佢諗唔到送咩俾我<br />\n佢都係直接問我想收咩禮物<br />\n然後買嚟畀我<br />\n雖然嗰份驚喜係冇咗<br />\n但至少我可以一直帶喺身邊<br />\n一見到嗰樣嘢就諗起佢<br />\n啲frd 問起又可以俾佢間接宣示主權<br />\n所以我覺得與其買一份唔知啱唔啱對方心水嘅禮物<br />\n咁樣唔係仲好咩<br />\n定係係我個人奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93552f8241ab8467742ab4d71c356ac7c4efc0c2","tid":1020852,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d29d1f7251480f780014e29bbb894e7119becc46","tid":1020852,"uid":207166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32406d11cda41ca19b98ba24e4136def767eec9d","tid":1020852,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:04:55.000Z","msg":"講到明要咩禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:10:51.000Z","msg":"之前聖誕佢諗唔到送咩俾我<br />\n佢都係直接問我想收咩禮物<br />\n然後買嚟畀我<br />\n雖然嗰份驚喜係冇咗<br />\n但至少我可以一直帶喺身邊<br />\n一見到嗰樣嘢就諗起佢<br />\n啲frd 問起又可以俾佢間接宣示主權<br />\n所以我覺得與其買一份唔知啱唔啱對方心水嘅禮物<br />\n咁樣唔係仲好咩<br />\n定係係我個人奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:11:39.000Z","msg":"其實我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 送完佢唔岩又好似局住要咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c74fc8a796399a925036d5f2ad064bdcc1c67d6","tid":1020852,"uid":207166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f45dd5cddd1ae80f5c1c6376f64a30b6cc006e6c","tid":1020852,"uid":211060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:09:01.000Z","msg":"香水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T01:13:45.000Z","msg":"佢細我5年，中學師妹嚟<br />\n而家Form 6，所以好少會化妝<br />\n而香水佢已經有唔少<br />\n而且我之前講過我鍾意佢素顏多啲<